name: Brett's Dog
description: Introducing... BROGG!!! Brogg is based on an original Matt Furie design which was left unnamed. So we adopted him, gave him a home, and found him an owner... Brett! And now, Brogg is on Base, following his master, to herald a new generation of dog tokens on the chain. Brogg is here to prove that he can be the alpha dog in the Base Chain yard!
